âœ… Why Use Trivy Alone?
| Feature                       | Trivy Capability                              |
| ----------------------------- | --------------------------------------------- |
| ğŸ” Static code analysis (IaC) | âœ… Scans Terraform, Dockerfiles, etc.          |
| ğŸ³ Container image scan       | âœ… Finds OS + language package vulnerabilities |
| ğŸ” Secrets detection          | âœ… Detects hardcoded secrets in your code      |
| ğŸ“¦ Dependency scanning (SCA)  | âœ… Detects CVEs in `pip`, `npm`, etc.          |
